  Section 9: Stats Section — 3 large stat blocks
  Social proof through numbers. Builds belief through specificity.
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="stats-section">
  <div class="stats-section__inner page-width">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-block">
        <span class="stat-block__number">88%</span>
        <span class="stat-block__text">said pain noticeably reduced in the first 1–2 weeks — not masked, actually reduced</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-block">
        <span class="stat-block__number">92%</span>
        <span class="stat-block__text">could do things they'd given up on — bending, walking, cooking, playing with grandkids</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-block">
        <span class="stat-block__number">91%</span>
        <span class="stat-block__text">slept better and woke up without dreading the first step out of bed</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="stats-section__disclaimer">Based on customer survey of 500+ [BRAND]™ users after 30 days of consistent use.</p>
  </div>
</div>

